claim.claim-text:
Modular shelving (10) comprising
- at least two shelves (20), arranged horizontally;
- at least two uprights (30), arranged vertically between said two shelves (20); and
- an attachment system (40, 31, 21) between said uprights (30) and said shelves (20),
characterised in that said attachment system comprises
- at least one fastening element (40) fixed to each of said uprights;
- a major horizontal profile (21), stably fixed to each of said shelves (20), said major profile comprising at least one grooved guide (22, 23) suitable for partially housing said at least one fastening element (40);
- a vertical minor profile (31), stably fixed to each of said uprights (30) and suitable for partially housing said at least one fastening element (40).
